<i>adjective</i>: 보슬보슬하다 [보슬보슬하다], 버석하다 [버서카다], 버석버석하다 [버석뻐서카다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>보슬보슬하다 [보슬보슬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>crumbly</dd><br>
<dd>물기가 적은 것이 잘 뭉치지 않고 잘게 부서지기 쉬운 상태이다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in a state in which something with little moisture is not kneaded into a lump and easily crumbles.</dd><br>
<dt>버석하다 [버서카다]</dt><br>
<dd>crisp; crumbly; friable</dd><br>
<dd>너무 말라서 잘게 부스러질 만큼 물기가 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>So dry without moisture as to crumble into small pieces.</dd><br>
<dt>버석버석하다 [버석뻐서카다]</dt><br>
<dd>crisp; crumbly; friable</dd><br>
<dd>너무 말라서 잘게 부스러질 만큼 물기가 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>So dry without moisture as to crumble into small pieces.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>